summary: Baby Bonk - Baby Bonk intends to follow his father’s footsteps and leave a unique mark in the crypto space. The Baby Bonk contributors were tired of Binance FUD and wanted to make a fun memecoin where everyone gets a fair shot. Baby Bonk Coin is a deflationary token that launched fairly by the dog-loving team and community on the BNB Chain, with an in-built auto reflection system and staking rewards dApp for all its holders.
